From: amphetamine <amphetamine@triskelion>
Subject: configure: register lsteamclient DLL in Wine build system

Adds WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE entry so lsteamclient builds as a Wine DLL.
Source symlinked from Proton's lsteamclient/ into dlls/lsteamclient/.
Requires autoconf regeneration after applying.

---
diff --git a/configure.ac b/configure.ac
index 33860c12462..7ae12031d11 100644
--- a/configure.ac
+++ b/configure.ac
@@ -2830,6 +2830,7 @@ WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/localui)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/localui/tests)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/lz32)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/lz32/tests)
+WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/lsteamclient)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/lzexpand.dll16,enable_win16)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/magnification)
 WINE_CONFIG_MAKEFILE(dlls/mapi32)
